TextView.android:text:
Rule 1) Always set a item with 'selected = true'. So you can easy get data selected in memory without touch UI; 

Rule 2) Doesn't trigger default/first ID; 

Rule 3) Doesn't trigger when default value is selected; 

Rule 4) You can easy customize item/row creating your own 'adapter_spinnable.xml';

Rule 5) 'Default string' it isn't counted as index.
